<center><h1>Welcome to Discussion Group</h1></center>
Home page maintained by the host of Discussion Group. For more information please send inquiry to host.
 <p>
<a href="http://www.cs.pitt.edu/~chang/231/cgi-bin/bu.html"><b>The Bulletin Board</b></a>  Members can post messages here<br><p>
<b>If you want to send or post a message, please provide the following information.
You must enter your name, but the other fields are optional.  You can send
a private message to the host.  You can send e-mail message to all members
and the message will also be posted.  Finally, you can post a message on the
bulletin board, without sending e-mail message to all members.
When you click on "Submit", your message will be sent or posted!</b>
(If you try to post to the bulletin board and see an error message, often your message has already
been posted, even with an error message!  Therefore, please check
the bulletin board first.  If your posted message is not there, then
resubmit.)
